title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Whats truly meant for you, few can deny. Of course, you must have the daring to go get it. Youre liable to be impatient taking baby steps toward a big goal, so you might push yourself harder or even skip an important step for faster results. Deep inside, you know this shortcut is likely a mistake, but you want the future now. Nevertheless, all of nature points to the fact that you must grow in stages to achieve what you desire. Time will stay on your side if you are willing to act with patience and perseverance. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
